Overlay for porting MIUI to the HTC Evo
Original froyo overlay by bcnice20
updated gingerbread overlay by me

framework.jar instructions:
Use baksmali to decomiple classes.dex from original MIUI framework.jar
Overwrite two files from overlay in respective directory
Use smali to recompile classes.dex and insert in MIUI framework.jar

framework-res.apk instructions:
Replace eri.xml in MIUI framework-res.apk/res/xml/ with file from overlay

7/18/2011
Initial commit of overlay


7/18/2011
 - Fix ramdisk to allow FM Radio (Credit: Lithid)

 - In boot.img-ramdisk/init.supersonic.rc
Add to end:
service fmradio /system/bin/fmradioserver
    group bluetooth net_bt_admin


7/19/2011
Touched up build.prop for Rom Manager detection
Added GoogleQuickSearchBox.apk and MIUI.us_Forums_1.1.2_AdSupported.apk to /system/app


9/27/2011
 - Remove lib file causing bootloops
 - In boot.img-ramdisk/init.rc
Add last line:
service netd /system/bin/netd
    socket netd stream 0660 root system
    socket dnsproxyd stream 0660 root inet
